title: Yay Donald Glover, Rude Boy Giuliani Can’t Stop Failing 5.7.18

description:
In episode 142, Jack and Miles are joined by comedian Fahim Anwar to discuss Rudy Giuliani continuing to put his foot in his mouth, Don Blankenship's West Virginia senate nomination, Trump's sketchy golf course money that probably came from Russia, DJ Khaled refusing to perform cunnilingus on his wife, Lebron and his buzzer shot, Donald Glover's amazing new music video, the huge party that is the Kentucky Derby, and more!
